Atlas-derived data files in this directory
==========================================

The slice PNG images, annotation_100um.u32.bin, structures.json,
brain_surface_dv_idx.json / .npy, brain_bottom_dv_idx.npy and
coords.json are derived from the Allen Mouse Brain Common Coordinate
Framework (CCFv3), retrieved via brainglobe-atlasapi.

